Private Parties Reviews review by - Yelp Deborah B: This gem is a great addition to Johns Island. The staff is courteous, efficient and friendly. The food is outstanding and there are a variety of options for cocktails. The atmosphere is perfect for every member of the family to enjoy from the televisions with sports to the amusements for both adults and children. The Natural is definitely a great experience for locals and guests. review by - Google Chris R: I am blown away by this place. Everything from the plaza it is located in and the patio to the interior - the bar, the arcade area, the seating - everything is exquisitely clean, fresh, and a great vibe.
